commit.title: Another micro-improvement in printing "fix".
commit.message:
Another micro-improvement in printing "fix".

Inductive option A := None | Some (a:A).
Coercion some_nat := @Some nat.
Notation nnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnn := nat.
Notation bbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbb := bool.
Set Printing Width 20.
Check fix fffffffffffffff xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx (aaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaa:nat) (ccccccccccccccccccc:bool) :=
  match xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx with 0 => None _ | n => some_nat n end.

gives:

fix
  fffffffffffffff
  (xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx
   aaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaa : nnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnn)
  (ccccccccccccccccccc : bbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbb)
  {struct
   xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx} :
    option
      nnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnn :=
  match
    xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx
  with
  | 0 =>
      None
        nnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnnn
  | S _ =>
      some_nat
        xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx
  end
